#: ../../source/manage_data/2. datasource.md:1
msgid "本地数据源——DataSource对象"
msgstr "Local data source — DataSource object"

#: ../../source/manage_data/2. datasource.md:3
msgid ""
"本地数据源是`qteasy`数据管理功能的核心，所有的数据都必须首先下载并保存在本地数据源中，才能为`qteasy`所用。`qteasy`使用`DataSource`对象管理本地数据源，本地数据源类似于一个数据库，包含一系列预先定义的数据表，`DataSource`类提供了一系列API用于数据表中数据的管理，包括读取、更新、删除和查询其中的数据。"
msgstr ""
"The local data source is the core of `qteasy`'s data management "
"functionality. All data must first be downloaded and saved in the local data"
" source before it can be used by `qteasy`. `qteasy` uses `DataSource` "
"objects to manage the local data source. The local data source is similar to"
" a database, containing a series of predefined data tables. The `DataSource`"
" class provides a series of APIs for managing the data in the data tables, "
"including reading, updating, deleting, and querying data."

#: ../../source/manage_data/2. datasource.md:5
msgid "要创建一个新的`DataSource`对象，可以使用下面的命令："
msgstr ""
"To create a new `DataSource` object, you can use the following command:"

#: ../../source/manage_data/2. datasource.md:12
msgid "通过打印`DataSource`对象，可以查看其最基本的属性："
msgstr ""
"By printing the `DataSource` object, you can view its most basic properties:"

#: ../../source/manage_data/2. datasource.md:19
msgid "从`DataSource`的打印字符串`file://csv@qt_root/data/`中，可以看出它的基本属性"
msgstr ""
"From the printed string `file://csv@qt_root/data/` of `DataSource`, we can "
"see its basic properties."

#: ../../source/manage_data/2. datasource.md:21
msgid "打印结果包含数据源对象的基本信息："
msgstr ""
"The printed results contain basic information about the data source object:"

#: ../../source/manage_data/2. datasource.md:22
msgid ""
"`file:` -- "
"数据源的类型。`qteasy`支持两种类型的数据源：文件型和数据库型，`file`代表数据源中的所有数据表都是以文件的形式保存在磁盘上的，同样，数据也可以保存在`mysql`数据库中，此时数据源的类型代码为`db`。"
msgstr ""
"`file:` -- The type of data source. `qteasy` supports two types of data "
"sources: file-based and database-based. `file` means that all data tables in"
" the data source are stored on disk as files. Similarly, data can also be "
"stored in a `mysql` database, in which case the data source type code is "
"`db`."

#: ../../source/manage_data/2. datasource.md:23
msgid ""
"`csv:` -- "
"数据文件保存格式。`qteasy`可以将数据文件以不同的格式保存在磁盘上，最基本的格式为`csv`文件，但是用户同样可以将数据保存为`hdf`文件和`fth`文件（`feather`文件)，以满足不同的性能偏好。"
msgstr ""
"`csv:` -- Data file saving format. `qteasy` can save data files to disk in "
"different formats. The most basic format is `csv`, but users can also save "
"data as `hdf` and `fth` (`feather`) files to meet different performance "
"preferences."

#: ../../source/manage_data/2. datasource.md:24
msgid ""
"`qt_root/data/:` -- "
"数据文件的保存路径。其中`qt_root`表示`qteasy`的安装根路径，默认情况下所有数据文件都保存在根目录下的`/data/`子路径下"
msgstr ""
"`qt_root/data/:` -- The path to save data files. `qt_root` represents the "
"installation root path of `qteasy`. By default, all data files are saved in "
"the `/data/` subdirectory under the root directory."

#: ../../source/manage_data/2. datasource.md:26
msgid ""
"同样，可以创建一个数据保存类型为数据库的数据源对象，并查看其基本属性: "
"不过，创建类型为数据库的数据源时，需要指定需要连接的Mysql数据库的主机名、用户名、密码、（或者）数据库名称等信息:"
msgstr ""
"Similarly, you can create a data source object with the data storage type "
"\"database\" and view its basic properties. However, when creating a data "
"source of type \"database\", you need to specify the hostname, username, "
"password, and/or database name of the MySQL database you want to connect to."

#: ../../source/manage_data/2. datasource.md:35
msgid "同样，打印结果中包含数据源的基本信息："
msgstr ""
"Similarly, the printed results contain basic information about the data "
"source:"

#: ../../source/manage_data/2. datasource.md:36
msgid "`db:mysql` -- 数据源的类型为mysql数据库，所有的数据表都保存在数据库中"
msgstr ""
"`db:mysql` -- The data source type is a MySQL database; all data tables are "
"stored in this database."

#: ../../source/manage_data/2. datasource.md:37
msgid "`localhost` -- 数据库的主机名"
msgstr "`localhost` -- the hostname of the database"

#: ../../source/manage_data/2. datasource.md:38
msgid "`3306` -- 数据库连接端口"
msgstr "`3306` -- Database connection port"

#: ../../source/manage_data/2. datasource.md:39
msgid "`test_db` -- 数据库名称，如果不指定名称，默认数据库`qt_db`，不过这个数据库必须事先创建好"
msgstr ""
"`test_db` -- Database name. If no name is specified, the default database is"
" `qt_db`, but this database must be created beforehand."

#: ../../source/manage_data/2. datasource.md:41
msgid ""
"不同的数据源对象，如果它们的存储方式不同，存储路径不同，那么它们所保存的数据没有关系，互不干扰，但如果两个数据源指向同一个路径，且文件类型相同时，那么它们所保存的数据就会重复。"
msgstr ""
"Different data source objects, if they have different storage methods and "
"storage paths, will have no relationship with each other and will not "
"interfere with each other's data. However, if two data sources point to the "
"same path and have the same file type, then they will store duplicate data."

#: ../../source/manage_data/2. datasource.md:43
msgid "要查看数据源的更多基本属性，可以调用数据源对象的几个属性查看："
msgstr ""
"To view more basic properties of the data source, you can access several "
"properties of the data source object:"

#: ../../source/manage_data/2. datasource.md:56
msgid "默认数据源"
msgstr "Default data source"

#: ../../source/manage_data/2. datasource.md:58
msgid ""
"`qteasy`有一个内置默认的数据源，不需要用户手动创建，默认情况下，所有的数据都会保存到这个默认数据源，并从这个数据源读取。用户可以通过`qteasy`的配置文件配置该数据源的参数，确保该数据源指向正确的路径或使用正确的用户名登陆正确的数据库。通过下面的方法查看内置默认数据源的属性："
msgstr ""
"`qteasy` has a built-in default data source that doesn't require manual "
"creation by the user. By default, all data is saved to and read from this "
"default data source. Users can configure the parameters of this data source "
"through `qteasy`'s configuration file, ensuring that the data source points "
"to the correct path or that the correct username is used to log in to the "
"correct database. The properties of the built-in default data source can be "
"viewed using the following method:"

#: ../../source/manage_data/2. datasource.md:65
msgid "查看数据表"
msgstr "View data table"

#: ../../source/manage_data/2. datasource.md:67
msgid "了解数据源对象的基本属性后，下一步可以进一步了解数据源中保存的数据。"
msgstr ""
"After understanding the basic properties of the data source object, the next"
" step is to further understand the data stored in the data source."

#: ../../source/manage_data/2. datasource.md:69
msgid ""
"数据源中的数据表都是事先定义好的，每一张数据表都保存一类不同的数据，这些数据涵盖沪深股市、期货市场的股票、指数、基金、期货、期权等各种不同投资产品的基本信息、K线行情、上市公司业绩报表、宏观经济数据等等大量的数据，完整的数据表清单介绍，请参见下一章节，这里主要介绍如何查看各种数据表的基本情况和数据。"
msgstr ""
"The data tables in the data source are all predefined. Each data table "
"stores a different type of data. This data covers a large amount of data, "
"including basic information, K-line data, listed company performance "
"reports, macroeconomic data, and so on for various investment products such "
"as stocks, indices, funds, futures, and options in the Shanghai and Shenzhen"
" stock markets and futures markets. For a complete list of data tables, "
"please see the next chapter. This section mainly introduces how to view the "
"basic information and data of various data tables."

#: ../../source/manage_data/2. datasource.md:71
msgid ""
"数据源中的数据表清单可以通过数据源的`all_tables`属性获取，它会返回一个列表对象，包含数据源中已经预定义的所有数据表。不过，这里必须厘清一个概念，数据源中虽然已经定义好了很多数据表，但这些数据表仅仅是有了基本的定义，即表头信息，数据表的字段名称、每个字段的含义以及数据类型都定义好了，但是刚刚建立的新数据源，其数据表往往都是空的，还没有任何数据。如果要查看数据源中有哪些数据表已经有了数据，需要用`get_table_info()`函数来获取："
msgstr ""
"The list of tables in a data source can be obtained through the data "
"source's `all_tables` property, which returns a list object containing all "
"predefined tables in the data source. However, it's crucial to clarify that "
"while many tables are defined in the data source, they only have basic "
"definitions: header information, field names, field meanings, and data types"
" are all defined. Newly created data sources typically have empty tables "
"containing no data. To see which tables in the data source already contain "
"data, you need to use the `get_table_info()` function."

#: ../../source/manage_data/2. datasource.md:79
msgid "可见，目前版本的`qteasy`预定义了108张数据表，其中部分数据表的名称包括`stock_basic`等。"
msgstr ""
"As can be seen, the current version of `qteasy` predefines 108 data tables, "
"some of which have names such as `stock_basic`."

#: ../../source/manage_data/2. datasource.md:81
msgid "如果要查看当前数据源中某张数据表的详情，例如该数据表的定义，是否包含数据等信息，使用`get_table_info()`方法获取："
msgstr ""
"To view details of a specific table in the current data source, such as its "
"definition and whether it contains data, use the `get_table_info()` method."

#: ../../source/manage_data/2. datasource.md:112
msgid "打印的信息包括数据表的名称、说明、数据表的字段定义以及数据类型。"
msgstr ""
"The printed information includes the table name, description, field "
"definitions, and data types."

#: ../../source/manage_data/2. datasource.md:114
msgid "值得说明的是，如果数据表中已经填充了数据，那么就会显示出数据表目前的大小，在上面的例子中，一些关键信息的解释如下："
msgstr ""
"It's worth noting that if the data table is already populated with data, it "
"will display the current size of the table. In the example above, some key "
"information is explained below:"

#: ../../source/manage_data/2. datasource.md:116
msgid "`852KB/5K records on disc` -- 表示数据表占用磁盘空间大约852K字节，且数据量大约为5000行"
msgstr ""
"`852KB/5K records on disc` -- This indicates that the table occupies "
"approximately 852KB of disk space and contains approximately 5000 rows of "
"data."

#: ../../source/manage_data/2. datasource.md:117
msgid ""
"`primary keys` -- "
"显示数据的主键列，这里表示`ts_code`列为数据表的主键，且该列大约有5396条不同的记录。如果数据表有多个主键，那么每个主键列都分别列出，同时会列出该字段数据的范围，例如上例中`ts_code`列数据范围就是从`000001.SZ`开始一直到`920128.BJ`为止，让我们知道股票基本信息表里包含了代码从000001一直到920128为止的共五千多只股票的信息"
msgstr ""
"`primary keys` -- Displays the primary key columns of the data. Here, it "
"indicates that the `ts_code` column is the primary key of the table, and "
"this column has approximately 5396 distinct records. If the table has "
"multiple primary keys, each primary key column will be listed separately, "
"along with the range of data for that field. For example, in the above "
"example, the range of data for the `ts_code` column is from `000001.SZ` to "
"`920128.BJ`, letting us know that the basic stock information table contains"
" information on more than 5,000 stocks with codes from 000001 to 920128."

#: ../../source/manage_data/2. datasource.md:118
msgid ""
"`columns of table` -- "
"这里显示数据表的字段定义，也就是数据表的`schema`。列出每一列的名称`columns`、数据类型`dtypes`以及说明信息`remarks`"
msgstr ""
"`columns of table` -- This displays the field definitions of the data table,"
" which is the table's `schema`. It lists the name `columns`, data type "
"`dtypes`, and descriptive information `remarks` for each column."

#: ../../source/manage_data/2. datasource.md:120
msgid ""
"另外，`get_table_info()`方法返回一个`dict`，同样包含该数据表的信息,可以将这些信息打印出来，与上述格式化信息对照了解："
msgstr ""
"Additionally, the `get_table_info()` method returns a `dict`, which also "
"contains information about the table. This information can be printed out "
"and compared with the formatted information described above for better "
"understanding."

#: ../../source/manage_data/2. datasource.md:127
msgid "查看数据源的整体信息"
msgstr "View overall information about the data source"

#: ../../source/manage_data/2. datasource.md:129
msgid ""
"通过上面的方法，我们可以查看每一张数据表的具体定义和已经填充的数据信息。同样，通过`overview()`方法，我们可以检查所有的数据表，并汇总出整个数据源的整体信息："
msgstr ""
"Use the methods above to inspect each table; `overview()` summarizes the "
"whole DataSource:"

#: ../../source/manage_data/2. datasource.md:145
msgid "查看整个数据源的总体信息，可能需要花费数分钟的时间，因为需要统计每张数据表的所有信息。"
msgstr ""
"Viewing the overall information of the entire data source may take several "
"minutes because it requires summarizing all the information from each data "
"table."

#: ../../source/manage_data/2. datasource.md:147
msgid ""
"在统计过程中，`qteasy`会显示一根进度条显示统计的进度，最终统计分析完成后，`qteasy`会将数据源中所有数据表的信息以DataFrame的形式返回，并打印出关键的信息。"
msgstr ""
"During overview, qteasy shows a progress bar, then returns a `DataFrame` of "
"all tables and prints key stats."

#: ../../source/manage_data/2. datasource.md:150
msgid ""
"上面的信息显示了数据源中有3张数据表已经有了数据，包括`trade_calendar`、`stock_basic`和`stock_daily`，并显示了这些数据表的数据量、占用磁盘空间、数据的起始日期��结束日期等信息。如果想查看所有数据表的信息，可以将返回的`DataFrame`打印出来："
msgstr ""
"The summary shows three populated tables — `trade_calendar`, `stock_basic`, "
"`stock_daily` — with row counts, disk usage, and start/end dates. Print the "
"returned `DataFrame` to see all tables:"

#: ../../source/manage_data/2. datasource.md:185
msgid "最重要的数据表"
msgstr "The most important data table"

#: ../../source/manage_data/2. datasource.md:187
msgid ""
"如果您是第一次使用`qteasy`，很可能数据源中的数据表都是空的，没有任何数据。通常这没有任何问题，因为`qteasy`的设计初衷就是极大地简化金融数据的获取和使用过程。"
msgstr ""
"On first use, tables are often empty — by design, qteasy simplifies "
"acquiring and using financial data."

#: ../../source/manage_data/2. datasource.md:189
msgid ""
"您可以非常容易地从网络数据提供商处获取最基本的数据。不过，虽然数据表中的数据可以是空的，但是有几张数据表却比其他的数据表更加重要，您应该优先将这几张数据表的数据填充完整，因为这几张数据表中的数据是很多其他数据表的基础，甚至是`qteasy`的运行基础："
msgstr ""
"Basic data is easy to download, but some tables are more critical — fill "
"them first because others depend on them and on qteasy itself:"

#: ../../source/manage_data/2. datasource.md:191
msgid ""
"`trade_calendar` -- "
"交易日历表，包含了所有交易所的交易日历信息，包括交易日、交易所代码、交易所名称等信息。可以说这是`qteasy`运行的基础，如果缺了这张表，`qteasy`的很多功能都将无法运行或者将降低效率。"
" "
"`qteasy`使用这张表中的数据来判断交易日，如果要下载其他的数据表，通常也必须通过交易日数据表来确定下载的起止日期，因此，这是您应该**绝对优先**填充的数据表。"
msgstr ""
"`trade_calendar` — Trading calendar for all exchanges (trading day, exchange"
" code/name). Core to qteasy: many features fail or slow without it. Used to "
"determine trading days and download date ranges — **fill this table first**."

#: ../../source/manage_data/2. datasource.md:192
msgid ""
"`stock_basic` -- "
"股票基本信息表，包含了所有上市股票的基本信息，包括股票代码、股票名称、上市日期、退市日期、所属行业、地域等信息。这张表是很多其他数据表的基础，例如股票日K线数据表、股票财务数据表等，因此，这也是您应该**优先**填充的数据表。"
msgstr ""
"`stock_basic` — Stock basics table with code, name, listing/delisting dates,"
" industry, region, etc. Foundation for stock daily K-line and financial "
"tables; **prioritize** filling this table."

#: ../../source/manage_data/2. datasource.md:193
msgid ""
"`index_basic` -- "
"指数基本信息表，包含了所有指数的基本信息，包括指数代码、指数名称、发布日期、退市日期等信息。这张表是很多其他数据表的基础，例如指数日K线数据表、指数成分股表等，因此，这也是您应该**优先**填充的数据表。"
msgstr ""
"`index_basic` — Index basics table with code, name, publish/delisting dates,"
" etc. Foundation for index daily K-line and constituent tables; "
"**prioritize** filling this table."

#: ../../source/manage_data/2. datasource.md:194
msgid ""
"`fund_basic` -- "
"基金基本信息表，包含了所有基金的基本信息，包括基金代码、基金名称、基金类型、基金规模等信息。这张表是很多其他数据表的基础，例如基金日K线数据表、基金净值数据表等，因此，这也是您应该**优先**填充的数据表。"
msgstr ""
"`fund_basic` — Fund basics table with code, name, type, size, etc. "
"Foundation for fund daily K-line and NAV tables; **prioritize** filling this"
" table."

#: ../../source/manage_data/2. datasource.md:196
msgid "基本上，如果您能够填充了上面这几张数据表的数据，那么您就可以开始比较顺畅使用`qteasy`的大部分数据相关的功能了。"
msgstr ""
"Once these key tables are filled, most qteasy data features work smoothly."

#: ../../source/manage_data/2. datasource.md:198
msgid "另外，`qteasy`还在数据源中定义了几张系统数据表，这些表一共四张，用于存储跟实盘交易相关的信息："
msgstr "qteasy also defines four system tables for live-trading records:"

#: ../../source/manage_data/2. datasource.md:200
msgid ""
"`sys_op_live_accounts` -- "
"实盘交易账户信息表，包含了所有实盘交易账户的基本信息，包括账户ID、账户名称、账户类型、账户状态等信息。"
msgstr ""
"`sys_op_live_accounts` — Live trading account master table with account ID, "
"name, type, status, etc."

#: ../../source/manage_data/2. datasource.md:201
msgid ""
"`sys_op_positions` -- 实盘持仓信息表，包括所有实盘交易账户的持仓信息，包括账户ID、证券代码、证券名称、持仓数量、持仓成本等信息。"
msgstr ""
"`sys_op_positions` — Live positions table with account ID, security "
"code/name, quantity, cost, etc."

#: ../../source/manage_data/2. datasource.md:202
msgid ""
"`sys_op_trade_orders` -- "
"实盘交易委托表，包括所有实盘交易账户的交易委托信息，包括账户ID、委托时间、委托类型、证券代码、委托数量、委托价格等信息。"
msgstr ""
"`sys_op_trade_orders` — Live order table with account ID, order time/type, "
"security code, quantity, price, etc."

#: ../../source/manage_data/2. datasource.md:203
msgid ""
"`sys_op_trade_results` -- "
"实盘交易成交表，包括所有实盘交易账户的交易成交信息，包括账户ID、成交时间、证券代码、成交数量、成交价格等信息。"
msgstr ""
"`sys_op_trade_results` — Live fill table with account ID, fill time, "
"security code, quantity, price, etc."

#: ../../source/manage_data/2. datasource.md:205
msgid "上面四张表是qteasy实盘交易功能的基础，这几张表中的数据不需要人为填充，而是系统自动生成，您不需要查看、填充或删除这些表"
msgstr ""
"These four system tables underpin live trading; data is auto-generated — do "
"not manually fill, view, or delete them."

#: ../../source/manage_data/2. datasource.md:207
msgid "其他的数据表"
msgstr "Other tables"

#: ../../source/manage_data/2. datasource.md:209
msgid ""
"除了上面提到的几张重要的数据表之外，数据源中还定义了大量的数据表，这些数据表包含了各种各样的金融数据，包括股票、指数、基金、期货、期权等各种金融产品的基本信息、日K线数据、财务数据、分红数据、业绩报表、宏观经济数据等等，主要分类如下："
msgstr ""
"Besides key tables, DataSource defines many more covering basics, daily "
"K-line, financials, dividends, earnings reports, macro data, etc.:"

#: ../../source/manage_data/2. datasource.md:211
msgid "行情数据表 -- 这类数据表包含了股票、基金、指数各个不同频率的K线行情数据"
msgstr ""
"Market data tables — OHLCV at various frequencies for stocks, funds, indices"

#: ../../source/manage_data/2. datasource.md:212
msgid "基本信息表 -- 这类数据表包含了股票、基金、指数、期货、期权等各种金融产品的基本信息"
msgstr "Basics tables — stocks, funds, indices, futures, options, etc."

#: ../../source/manage_data/2. datasource.md:213
msgid "指标信息表 -- 这类数据表包含了各种指标的信息，例如技术指标、基本面指标、宏观经济指标等"
msgstr "Indicator tables — technical, fundamental, macro indicators, etc."

#: ../../source/manage_data/2. datasource.md:214
msgid "财务数据表 -- 这类数据表包含了上市公司的财务报表数据，包括资产负债表、利润表、现金流量表等"
msgstr ""
"Financial statement tables — balance sheet, income statement, cash flow, "
"etc."

#: ../../source/manage_data/2. datasource.md:215
msgid "业绩报表表 -- 这类数据表包含了上市公司的业绩报表数据，包括业绩快报、业绩预告、业绩预测等"
msgstr ""
"Earnings report tables — express reports, earnings guidance, forecasts, etc."

#: ../../source/manage_data/2. datasource.md:216
msgid "分红交易数据表 -- 这类数据表包含了上市公司的分红数据，以及股票大宗交易、股东交易等信息表"
msgstr ""
"Dividend & block-trade tables — dividends, block trades, shareholder trades,"
" etc."

#: ../../source/manage_data/2. datasource.md:217
msgid "参考数据表 -- 这类数据表包含了各种参考数据，例如宏观经济数据、行业数据、交易所数据等"
msgstr ""
"Reference tables — macro, industry, exchange, and other reference data"

#: ../../source/manage_data/2. datasource.md:219
msgid "这些数据表的具体定义和数据类型，可以通过`get_table_info()`方法查看，或者通过本文档的下一章节查询。"
msgstr ""
"See `get_table_info()` or the next chapter for table definitions and data "
"types."

#: ../../source/manage_data/2. datasource.md:221
msgid "从数据表中获取数据"
msgstr "Reading data from tables"

#: ../../source/manage_data/2. datasource.md:223
msgid ""
"如果数据表中已经填充了数据，那么现在就可以从中读取数据了。`DataSource`提供了`read_table_data()`方法，从数据源中直接读取某个数据表中的数据，同时，用户可以筛选数据的起止日期以及证券代码，同时不用考虑数据表的具体结构、存储方式、存储位置等具体的实现方式。"
msgstr ""
"Once filled, use `read_table_data()` to read with date/code filters without "
"worrying about storage details."

#: ../../source/manage_data/2. datasource.md:225
msgid ""
"为了避免读取的数据量过大，建议在读取数据时一定要同时给出某些筛选条件。对于`read_table_data()`方法来说，用户总是可以通过证券代码和起止日期来筛选数据:"
msgstr ""
"To avoid huge reads, always pass filters. With `read_table_data()` you can "
"filter by security code and date range:"

#: ../../source/manage_data/2. datasource.md:227
msgid "***`shares`***: 给出一个证券代码或者逗号分隔的多个证券代码，如果数据表的主键中含有证券代码，那么根据该证券代码筛选输出的数据"
msgstr ""
"***`shares`***: One security code or comma-separated codes. If the primary "
"key includes a security code, filter output by those codes"

#: ../../source/manage_data/2. datasource.md:228
msgid ""
"***`start`***: "
"给出一个日期，格式为`“YYYYMMDD”`，如果数据表的主键包含时间或日期，那么根据筛选`start`与`end`之间的数据，`start/end`必须成对给出"
msgstr ""
"***`start`***: A date in `“YYYYMMDD”` format. If the table primary key "
"includes time or date, filter rows between `start` and `end`; `start`/`end` "
"must be provided as a pair"

#: ../../source/manage_data/2. datasource.md:229
msgid ""
"***`end`***: "
"给出一个日期，格式为`“YYYYMMDD”`，如果数据表的主键包含时间或日期，那么根据筛选`start`与`end`之间的数据，`start/end`必须成对给出"
msgstr ""
"***`end`***: A date in `“YYYYMMDD”` format. If the table primary key "
"includes time or date, filter rows between `start` and `end`; `start`/`end` "
"must be provided as a pair"

#: ../../source/manage_data/2. datasource.md:231
msgid "`DataSource`对象会根据输入的筛选条件自动筛选数据，例如："
msgstr ""
"`DataSource` filters data automatically from your criteria, for example:"

#: ../../source/manage_data/2. datasource.md:233
msgid "从`stock_daily`表中读取一只股票（`000651.SZ`）从2024年1月1日到2024年1月15日之间的股票日K线数据："
msgstr ""
"Read daily K-line data for `000651.SZ` from `stock_daily` between 2024-01-01"
" and 2024-01-15:"

#: ../../source/manage_data/2. datasource.md:253
msgid ""
"`DataSource`对象会自动根据数据表的定义来进行正确的筛选，并忽略掉不必要的参数。例如，我们可以筛选出某两支股票的基本信息。对于股票基本信息来说，交易日期是个不必要的参数，此时`qteasy`会自动忽略掉`start`/`end`参数并给出提示信息。同样，`shares`参数也不一定只能匹配股票代码，对于基金、指数、甚至期货、期权，都可以同样匹配："
msgstr ""
"`DataSource` applies the correct filters for each table and ignores "
"unnecessary parameters. For example, when querying basic info for two "
"stocks, trade date is not required — `qteasy` ignores `start`/`end` with a "
"notice. The `shares` parameter also works for funds, indices, futures, and "
"options, not just stocks:"

#: ../../source/manage_data/2. datasource.md:269
msgid "关于`read_table_data()`方法的更多信息，请参阅`DataSource`对象的参考信息。"
msgstr "See `DataSource` reference for more on `read_table_data()`."

#: ../../source/manage_data/2. datasource.md:271
msgid "向数据表中添加数据"
msgstr "Adding data to tables"

#: ../../source/manage_data/2. datasource.md:273
msgid "如果数据表中尚未填充数据，或者数据表中填充的数据不足以满足我们的需求，那么读取数据就会不成功。为了避免这种情况，我们需要向数据表中填充数据。"
msgstr "Reads fail if tables are empty or insufficient — fill tables first."

#: ../../source/manage_data/2. datasource.md:275
msgid "请注意："
msgstr "Note:"

#: ../../source/manage_data/2. datasource.md:277
msgid ""
"这里介绍的仅仅是向数据表中手动添加数据的基本方法。`qteasy`还提供了全自动数据下载、数据清洗、数据填充等功能，可以帮助用户自动从网络数据源中下载数据，并将数据整理、清洗、更新到数据表中。这些功能将在后续章节中介绍。"
msgstr ""
"This covers manual writes only; automatic download, cleaning, and refill are"
" covered later."

#: ../../source/manage_data/2. datasource.md:279
msgid ""
"向数据表中填充数据可以使用数据源的`update_table_data()`方法。使用这个API，用户可以将保存在一个`DataFrame`中的数据写入到相应的数据表中。这个API只需要给出三个参数："
msgstr ""
"Fill tables via `update_table_data()`, writing a `DataFrame` with three "
"parameters:"

#: ../../source/manage_data/2. datasource.md:281
msgid "***`table`***: 一个数据表的名称，需要写入数据的数据表"
msgstr "***`table`***: Name of the target table to write into"

#: ../../source/manage_data/2. datasource.md:282
msgid "***`df`***: 一个`DataFrame`，保存了需要写入数据表中的数据"
msgstr "***`df`***: A `DataFrame` holding data to write into a table"

#: ../../source/manage_data/2. datasource.md:283
msgid "***`merge_type`***: 如果是`update`则更新数据表中已经存在的数据，如果是`ignore`则忽略重复的数据."
msgstr ""
"***`merge_type`***: If `update`, update existing rows in the table; if "
"`ignore`, skip duplicate rows."

#: ../../source/manage_data/2. datasource.md:285
msgid ""
"使用`update_table_data()`方法，用户不需要保证写入的数据格式与数据表完全一致，只要数据格式与数据表大致一致，`qteasy`就会自动整理数据格式、删除重复数据，确保写入数据表中的数据符合要求。"
msgstr ""
"With `update_table_data()`, exact schema match is not required — qteasy "
"normalizes format and deduplicates before writing."

#: ../../source/manage_data/2. datasource.md:287
msgid "下面将一些示例数据写入数据源(写入的数据仅为演示效果)"
msgstr "Sample data is written below for demonstration only."

#: ../../source/manage_data/2. datasource.md:315
msgid ""
"上面的`DataFrame`中保存了一些示例数据，我们下面将把这个`DataFrame`的数据写入数据源中的`index_daily`数据表。 "
"目前我们可以看到，`index_daily`数据表是空的，而且这个数据表的`schema`与上面的`DataFrame`并不完全相同："
msgstr ""
"The sample `DataFrame` above will be written to `index_daily`. Currently "
"`index_daily` is empty and its `schema` differs slightly from the "
"`DataFrame`:"

#: ../../source/manage_data/2. datasource.md:318
msgid ""
"`index_daily`数据表的数据定义中包含11列，而上面的数据只有6列，不过`DataFrame`中的所有列都包含在`index_daily`数据表的`schema`中"
msgstr ""
"The `index_daily` table schema defines 11 columns while the sample "
"`DataFrame` above has only 6; all `DataFrame` columns are still within the "
"`index_daily` `schema`."

#: ../../source/manage_data/2. datasource.md:319
msgid "`index_daily`数据表目前是空的，没有填充任何数据"
msgstr "The `index_daily` table is currently empty with no data filled."

#: ../../source/manage_data/2. datasource.md:348
msgid "接下来我们可以将数据写入数据表，如果方法执行正确，它将返回写入数据表中的数据的行数，如下所示："
msgstr "Next we write data; on success the method returns rows written:"

#: ../../source/manage_data/2. datasource.md:354
msgid "将数据写入数据表之后，我们可以尝试一下从数据表中读取数据，现在我们已经可以读出刚才写入的数据了。"
msgstr "After writing, we can read back the data just inserted."

#: ../../source/manage_data/2. datasource.md:356
msgid ""
"请注意，读出来的数据有许多列都是`NaN`值，这表明这些列没有写入数据，原因就是我们写入的`df`并不包含这些数据，因此读出的数据为`NaN`值。"
msgstr ""
"Many columns read as `NaN` because the written `df` did not include those "
"fields."

#: ../../source/manage_data/2. datasource.md:376
msgid "删除数据表 —— 请尽量小心，删除后无法恢复！！"
msgstr "Drop table — be careful; deletion is irreversible!!"

#: ../../source/manage_data/2. datasource.md:378
msgid ""
"我们除了可以向数据表中写入数据，从数据表中读取数据之外，当然也可以删除数据，不过请注意，在`qteasy`中操作`DataSource`删除数据时，您务必非常小心：因为`qteasy`不支持从数据表中删除部分数据，您只能删除整张数据表。"
msgstr ""
"You can also drop entire tables — qteasy does not support partial deletes; "
"be very careful."

#: ../../source/manage_data/2. datasource.md:380
msgid ""
"这是因为`qteasy`的数据源被设计为高效地存储和读取数据，但它并不是一个通常的数据库，我们并不需要经常操作其中的数据，这个数据仓库的作用是为了存储巨量的数据，因此，它的重点在于保存和提取数据，而不是删除操作。"
msgstr ""
"DataSource is optimized for storage and reads, not frequent deletes — it is "
"a data warehouse, not a general database."

#: ../../source/manage_data/2. datasource.md:382
msgid ""
"`qteasy`的`DataSource`对象提供了一个删除数据表的方法: "
"`drop_table_data()`,这个方法将删除整个数据表，而且**删除后无法恢复**！"
msgstr ""
"The `DataSource` method `drop_table_data()` deletes an entire table and "
"**cannot be undone**!"

#: ../../source/manage_data/2. datasource.md:384
msgid ""
"为了避免在代码中误删除数据表，默认情况下`drop_table_data()`会导致错误，例如我们想删除之前写入临时数据的`index_daily`表："
msgstr ""
"To prevent accidental drops, `drop_table_data()` errors by default — e.g. "
"when dropping temporary `index_daily` data:"

#: ../../source/manage_data/2. datasource.md:404
msgid ""
"这时候我们需要修改数据源的`allow_drop_table`属性，将其修改为`True`，这样就可以删除数据表了，请记住删除后将`allow_drop_table`改为`False`。"
msgstr ""
"Set `allow_drop_table` to `True` to allow drops; set it back to `False` "
"afterwards."

#: ../../source/manage_data/2. datasource.md:406
msgid "下面代码删除了`index_daily`表，然后就会发现，无法从该表读取数据了："
msgstr ""
"The code below drops `index_daily`; afterwards reads from that table fail:"

